core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"聯同被中共迫害族群，合情合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948c5124690b3abac22af5d5056f2e0d685d8ab5","tid":1263921,"uid":78470,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:20:07.000Z","msg":"搞集中營唔應該制裁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdd00ffa9e45fea8c975d4abc8e8be2b79f5b424","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"有市民到美國和英國等領事館請願，要求外國停止干預香港事務。前香港民族黨召集人陳浩天就在日本大阪，促請國際社會制裁中國及香港。<br />\n<br />\n由市民眾籌集資刊登的反修訂《逃犯條例》廣告，繼續在多份外國報章出現，包括日本《朝日新聞》、《日本時報》；南韓的《朝鮮日報》、《韓國日報》和澳洲的《澳洲人報》等，目的是趁大阪二十國集團峰會，引起國際關注香港問題。<br />\n<br />\n早前被取締的「香港民族黨」召集人陳浩天到了大阪，促請各國制裁中國和香港。<br />\n<br />\n前香港民族黨召集人陳浩天表示：「香港政府正追隨北京的步伐，與整個文明世界對著幹。我在此促請所有國家聆聽，為了世界自由及文明，對中國及香港施以制裁。」<br />\n<br />\n同陳浩天同場的，還有「疆獨」組織、「世界維吾爾代表大會」主席熱比婭。<br />\n<br />\n在本港，約一百名市民響應網上號召，到美國、英國、德國總領事館及歐盟駐港辦事處請願，要求停止干預香港事務。<br />\n<br />\n林先生稱：「我們看見日前有部分香港市民出來表達意見，他們希望外國政府介入香港事務，甚至提出要求外國『解放香港』，我們認為這樣做是很危險的事。」<br />\n<br />\n各領事館和辦事處派代表接信。<br />\n<br />\n天仔原來叫郁埋香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed2506a5a979f9e7312dc88e87f32420dba60c6f","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:46:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355eabe4f7ff2d4f8f483bba928119c500559b4b","tid":1263921,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"佢話要制裁埋香港"},{"pid":"2797186bb500eba8a3b48f31ab29f8fddc1b09d8","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:54:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b3edcb4d29d75e6c378c3894bf82506d4eb550c","tid":1263921,"uid":265881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"死鳩開啦3毛 係咁POST 陳浩天做乜柒"},{"pid":"2959d92d9602796271707091ce79fb559a23e5a3","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4087558a3a2fbf02c97b6f8184d00bb9acdfaaf7","tid":1263921,"uid":60959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"355eabe4f7ff2d4f8f483bba928119c500559b4b","tid":1263921,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T12:47:10.000Z","msg":"佢話要制裁埋香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"係又點？"},{"pid":"7a5121659c0aece0287924a9344f870a32c07a6e","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:39:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce5e259e9e9ec1e269f95b1c4f1f78ae27fb2a3e","tid":1263921,"uid":203681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"林奠係咁撚口硬既高 焦唔焦土只係遲早既事"},{"pid":"dfdd6a1be284bfdacf50b42998fa775d508ab433","tid":1263921,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T13:54:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}